158
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,839
Hanchen.

159
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:31,040
Soal rekrut pelayan
untuk ruang baca,…

160
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:33,240
…jika Pangeran mau pulang ke Biandu,
maka abaikan saja.

161
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,160
Siapa bilang aku mau pulang?

162
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,679
Hanchen!

163
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,040
Kenapa kau pergi?

164
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,440
Jinguo sudah ketemu?

