Jangan sungkan.

178
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,519
Lao Xie, makan kepiting.

179
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:21,239
Namun, bukankah kalian harus…

180
00:08:21,239 --> 00:08:23,720
…mencari waktu mengunjungi
Tuan Xie Jing dulu?

181
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,760
Kami putuskan akan ke sana besok.

182
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,080
Besok, masih harus
merepotkan Minggu…

183
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:30,399
…membawa Xiaoman
langsung ke akademi.

184
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:32,520
Ada lagi.

185
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:35,159
Soal sekolah kedua anakku,…

186
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:38,060
…harus berterima kasih
pada Kakak dan Kakak Ipar.

187
00:08:38,060 --> 00:08:38,640
Benar.

188
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,840
Mari, bersulang untuk
Kakak dan Kakak Ipar.

189
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:41,919
Kakak Ipar.

190
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,450
Jangan sambil berdiri.

191
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:44,919
Duduk.

192
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:46,159
- Baik.
- Dasar.

193
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,760
Kita keluarga, tak perlu sungkan.

194
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:52,000
Ke depannya, tenang saja selama
Xiaoman tinggal di rumah kami.

195
00:08:52,359 --> 00:08:54,599
Aku pasti akan merawatnya
hingga gemuk.

196
00:08:55,239 --> 00:08:56,159
- Mari.
- Baik.

197
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:56,980
Terima kasih banyak.

198
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,039
Terima kasih, Kakak Ipar.

199
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:01,520
Ibu, kenapa aku harus
tinggal di sini?

200
00:09:01,599 --> 00:09:02,840
Apa aku tak pulang ke rumah?

201
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:04,039
Baik.

202
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:04,919
Mari, makan.

203
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:05,239
Mari.

204
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:06,679
Dasar miskin.

205
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:21,220
(Sajak klasik sumber kebijakan)

206
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:23,799
Ibu tahu kau tak mau tinggal
di Akademi Wu Jiang.

207
00:09:25,119 --> 00:09:27,280
Ibu tahu kau juga tak mau
tinggal di rumah paman.

208
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:29,000
Namun, kau juga tak pikir dulu.

209
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:31,400
Kakakmu ujian istana di Biandu.

210
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:33,919
Ayahmu juga bertugas
di Akademi Wu Jiang.

211
00:09:34,599 --> 00:09:36,450
Kau tak mungkin pulang
dan bercocok tanam, 'kan?

212
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:38,599
Kalau begitu, kenapa aku
harus tinggal di sini?

213
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,130
Aku ingin tinggal
dengan Ayah dan Ibu.

214
